    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[Description], [a].[Images], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[Name], [a].[Price], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreationTime] AS [CreationTime0], [a0].[CreatorUserId] AS [CreatorUserId0], [a0].[LastModificationTime] AS [LastModificationTime0], [a0].[LastModifierUserId] AS [LastModifierUserId0], [a0].[LastUpdated], [a0].[ProductId], [a0].[StockQuantity]
    FROM [AppProducts] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [AppStocks] AS [a0] ON [a].[Id] = [a0].[ProductId]
    WHERE [a0].[StockQuantity] > 0 AND LOWER([a].[Name]) LIKE @__ToLower_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN [AppCategories] AS [a1] ON [s].[CategoryId] = [a1].[Id]
ORDER BY [s].[CreationTime] DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a2].[Name], [a2].[Images] AS [Image], [a2].[Price], [a3].[Name] AS [CategoryName], COALESCE(SUM([a].[Quantity]), 0) AS [TotalSold]
FROM [AppOrderItems] AS [a]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[Status]
    FROM [AppOrders] AS [a0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [a1] ON [a].[OrderId] = [a1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AppProducts] AS [a2] ON [a].[ProductId] = [a2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AppCategories] AS [a3] ON [a2].[CategoryId] = [a3].[Id]
WHERE [a1].[Status] = N'Hoàn thành'
GROUP BY [a2].[Name], [a2].[Images], [a2].[Price], [a3].[Name]
ORDER BY COALESCE(SUM([a].[Quantity]), 0) DESC

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[Description], [a].[Images], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[Name], [a].[Price], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreationTime] AS [CreationTime0], [a0].[CreatorUserId] AS [CreatorUserId0], [a0].[LastModificationTime] AS [LastModificationTime0], [a0].[LastModifierUserId] AS [LastModifierUserId0], [a0].[LastUpdated], [a0].[ProductId], [a0].[StockQuantity]
    FROM [AppProducts] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN [AppStocks] AS [a0] ON [a].[Id] = [a0].[ProductId]
    WHERE [a0].[StockQuantity] > 0
    ORDER BY [a].[CreationTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN [AppCategories] AS [a1] ON [s].[CategoryId] = [a1].[Id]
ORDER BY [s].[CreationTime] DESC

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a2].[Name], [a2].[Images] AS [Image], [a2].[Price], [a3].[Name] AS [CategoryName], COALESCE(SUM([a].[Quantity]), 0) AS [TotalSold]
FROM [AppOrderItems] AS [a]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[Status]
    FROM [AppOrders] AS [a0]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [a1] ON [a].[OrderId] = [a1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AppProducts] AS [a2] ON [a].[ProductId] = [a2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AppCategories] AS [a3] ON [a2].[CategoryId] = [a3].[Id]
WHERE [a1].[Status] = N'Hoàn thành'
GROUP BY [a2].[Name], [a2].[Images], [a2].[Price], [a3].[Name]
ORDER BY COALESCE(SUM([a].[Quantity]), 0) DESC

    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
